# Repo layout: frontend/ (Next.js) | backend/ (FastAPI)
#
# Copy frontend/.env.example → frontend/.env.local
# Copy backend/.env.example  → backend/.env
#
# Docker Compose (from repo root):
#   docker compose up --build
# Optional: copy this file to .env and set LENDING_API_SECRET (and TrustIdLayer vars if not using mock).
# Compose wires LENDING_API_URL=http://backend:8000 inside the frontend container.
#
# If you see "dockerDesktopLinuxEngine: The system cannot find the file specified":
# start Docker Desktop and wait until it shows "Engine running", then run `docker info` to verify.
